Learning BNs - INSURANCE synthetic 500

Learning of BNs from augmented datasets created via deep generative models.

Get the libraries

library(bnlearn)
library(dplyr)
library(Rgraphviz)

Import the original data

df = read.csv("/Users/camilodavid/Downloads/insurance/insurance.csv")
df[sapply(df, is.character)] <- lapply(df[sapply(df, is.character)], 
                                       as.factor)

Original BN

modelstring = paste0("[Age][Mileage][SocioEcon|Age][GoodStudent|Age:SocioEcon]",
  "[RiskAversion|Age:SocioEcon][OtherCar|SocioEcon][VehicleYear|SocioEcon:RiskAversion]",
  "[MakeModel|SocioEcon:RiskAversion][SeniorTrain|Age:RiskAversion]",
  "[HomeBase|SocioEcon:RiskAversion][AntiTheft|SocioEcon:RiskAversion]",
  "[RuggedAuto|VehicleYear:MakeModel][Antilock|VehicleYear:MakeModel]",
  "[DrivingSkill|Age:SeniorTrain][CarValue|VehicleYear:MakeModel:Mileage]",
  "[Airbag|VehicleYear:MakeModel][DrivQuality|RiskAversion:DrivingSkill]",
  "[Theft|CarValue:HomeBase:AntiTheft][Cushioning|RuggedAuto:Airbag]",
  "[DrivHist|RiskAversion:DrivingSkill][Accident|DrivQuality:Mileage:Antilock]",
  "[ThisCarDam|RuggedAuto:Accident][OtherCarCost|RuggedAuto:Accident]",
  "[MedCost|Age:Accident:Cushioning][ILiCost|Accident]",
  "[ThisCarCost|ThisCarDam:Theft:CarValue][PropCost|ThisCarCost:OtherCarCost]")
original = model2network(modelstring)
graphviz.plot(original, shape = "ellipse")

score(original, df, type = "bic")
[1] -265884.4

Learn the BN structure with the synthetic data from stratified_500

BN_synth_500 <- tabu(synthetic_500)
Warning: variable Theft has levels that are not observed in the data.Warning: variable ILiCost has levels that are not observed in the data.
